title: Tootie, Booty & Boobies: Tootie's January 2015 Mix
description:
A new year, a new Tootie music mix. And this time, Tootie decided to add a title to the mix. Checking in at just under two hours, the highlight of "Tootie, Booty & Boobies: Tootie's January 2015 Mix" is a series of huge club joints from the mid-90s. But of course that's not all you'll hear.

All tracks are sourced from lossless material. All of the compilations' songs utilize playback gain values from Tootie's personal volume-leveling procedure, resulting in a consistent overall listening experience without the need to adjust the volume between songs. The method focuses on vocal volume.
